== Romanian ==
=== Etymology ===
From PIE *mend-, "horse", via a pre-Roman language. It is unanimously agreed to be [[cognate]] to the Thraacian word ''mezenai'', "horse", and Messapian ''Menzana'', a horse edity.
There is also an Albanian cognate, ''mëz''.

===Noun===
'''mânz'''
#[[colt]], young horse.

